{"tid":397754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法治] 為供兒子讀國際學校　女警前後欺詐11萬元　判12個月感化令","createTime":"2017-09-12T17:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T10:38:14.000Z","uid":43189,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bddfae4eefb164fafa73d478e321051fef10a721","tid":397754,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"一名女警聲稱為前夫還債及遭警方停薪，無錢為兒子繳交國際學校學費，決定編造故事誘使數人借錢，更盜用他人身分資料向財務公司借錢。女警早前承認4項欺詐罪，裁判官在西九龍裁判法院判刑時，指她極可能因為今次事件失去警隊工作，加上已經作出賠償，判她感化12個月。<br />\n<br />\n被告劉潔玲（44歲）1992年加入警隊，案發時隸屬於中區巡邏小隊。被告干犯首兩項詐騙罪，指她向兒子兩名同校家長編造謊話，分別借款3萬元及5萬元，後來被告已還清兩筆款項。另外兩項詐騙罪指，被告曾聲稱可以幫一名林姓事主申請其弟妹由內地移居香港，藉此取得對方身分資料。被告利用資料向財務公司申請3萬元貸款，林後來得悉事件報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n辯方曾透露，被告為了替就讀國際學校的兒子籌集學費才犯案，事後所有涉案款項已還清。辯方今再指其感化報告正面，被告有家人支持及須需要輔導。裁判官考慮她因本案極可能失去警隊工作，加上已經向事主作出賠償，判她感化12個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170912/s00001/1505196246888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170912%2Fs00001%2F1505196246888&d=l3iAGHHFDJc5PIMYmUveuP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a58a75ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170912%2Fs00001%2F1505196246888&h=4a36137c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170912/s00001/1505196246888</a><br />\n<br />\n紀律部隊知法犯法仲可以判輕啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad4c39bebbd0566cfbd65183f35ae98ae061a75","tid":397754,"uid":43189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T17:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170703/_2017070314393832110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170703%2F_2017070314393832110.jpg&h=e0e0dd9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"477d77edb1f81570e9d812e3dc9cd59fa750da14","tid":397754,"uid":144063,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T18:15:19.000Z","msg":"有個問題我想問好耐<br />\n老師同爸爸媽媽成日話警察叔叔係好人<br />\n但係我又成日見到新聞佢地女女女啊打市民啊果d<br />\n咁到底佢地係好人定壞人???<br />\n<br />\n利申:小學2年級 <br />\n大人唔應該呃小朋友 灌輸錯誤既觀念"},{"pid":"4bbf237449c4683de648a483269ca51438657c84","tid":397754,"uid":144063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T18:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54332d82ff1ac6f689ab4cf0d964f63e7adb61d0","tid":397754,"uid":22251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T18:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fc39ca4bf494e2e53266ebf486b4bb3a404eaa","tid":397754,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T23:16:03.000Z","msg":"即係仲未炒 每個月仲出緊幾皮野俾個黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6411356287daca30e2323f339c881eb9018529","tid":397754,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T23:19:37.000Z","msg":"休班警？"},{"pid":"89054083876420ccb696f579dc47f8dcd3cb869a","tid":397754,"uid":31323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T23:22:18.000Z","msg":"全港最大犯罪集團 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4114aeea0e9148b96d596e559f0a8f39740e166","tid":397754,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T23:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939ead31aac5d470f8ffa9b76ae64a3ffc64d54c","tid":397754,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T23:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全港最大犯罪集團 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全港最大犯罪集